  "detailed_description": "<h1>SPECIAL MESSAGE</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/084bc18501ef698cb0a875fd2da75695.poster.avif?t=1745014980\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/084bc18501ef698cb0a875fd2da75695.webm?t=1745014980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/084bc18501ef698cb0a875fd2da75695.mp4?t=1745014980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Dreadborne Dungeon</strong> is a stylized pixel art game that takes the player into an atmospheric retro world inspired by classics like Doom and Heretic. The game also borrows mechanics from Souls Like games and dungeon crawlers, offering a mix of retro shooters and challenges that require dexterity and strategic thinking.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Highlights:</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>STYLIZED GRAPHICS</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/530ccb7c7156446ead5b033fa23c7bdd.poster.avif?t=1745014980\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/530ccb7c7156446ead5b033fa23c7bdd.webm?t=1745014980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/530ccb7c7156446ead5b033fa23c7bdd.mp4?t=1745014980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The pixel art style pays homage to the golden age of video games, appealing to both fans of the classics and new players. Every detail, from dark dungeons to menacing enemies, is carefully designed to create a coherent and immersive atmosphere.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RETRO SHOOTER GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/ac254f593759fe4cb22e307f5c686120.poster.avif?t=1745014980\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/ac254f593759fe4cb22e307f5c686120.webm?t=1745014980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/ac254f593759fe4cb22e307f5c686120.mp4?t=1745014980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Simple classic shooting, limited only by the amount of ammo you have. Labyrinthine maps, keys and switches. Although the story may be minimalist, the game's atmosphere is built through the design of levels, enemies and music, which creates an immersive atmosphere.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SOULS LIKE ELEMENTS</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/souls-like.GIF?t=1745014980\" /></span><br><br>The game introduces mechanics typical of Souls Like games, such as challenging fights with enemies, a system of dying and learning from mistakes, and the need to develop effective strategies to defeat enemies and survive in a hostile world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DUNGEON EXPLORATION</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/76652c931ac83d1c1747af16ec435842.poster.avif?t=1745014980\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/76652c931ac83d1c1747af16ec435842.webm?t=1745014980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/76652c931ac83d1c1747af16ec435842.mp4?t=1745014980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Dreadborne Dungeon is also a classic dungeon crawler, in which players traverse dark dungeons. Each step can lead to new challenges and surprises.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SATISFACTORY DIFFICULTY</strong></h2>The game sets a high level of difficulty that rewards patience and determination. Every failure is an opportunity to learn and improve your skills, which gives great satisfaction from every success achieved.<br><br>Traverse dark dungeons, fight dangerous opponents and face numerous challenges. Die, draw conclusions and don't give up! Good luck!",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Dreadborne Dungeon</strong> is a stylized pixel art game that takes the player into an atmospheric retro world inspired by classics like Doom and Heretic. The game also borrows mechanics from Souls Like games and dungeon crawlers, offering a mix of retro shooters and challenges that require dexterity and strategic thinking.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Highlights:</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>STYLIZED GRAPHICS</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/530ccb7c7156446ead5b033fa23c7bdd.poster.avif?t=1745014980\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/530ccb7c7156446ead5b033fa23c7bdd.webm?t=1745014980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/530ccb7c7156446ead5b033fa23c7bdd.mp4?t=1745014980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The pixel art style pays homage to the golden age of video games, appealing to both fans of the classics and new players. Every detail, from dark dungeons to menacing enemies, is carefully designed to create a coherent and immersive atmosphere.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RETRO SHOOTER GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/ac254f593759fe4cb22e307f5c686120.poster.avif?t=1745014980\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/ac254f593759fe4cb22e307f5c686120.webm?t=1745014980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/ac254f593759fe4cb22e307f5c686120.mp4?t=1745014980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Simple classic shooting, limited only by the amount of ammo you have. Labyrinthine maps, keys and switches. Although the story may be minimalist, the game's atmosphere is built through the design of levels, enemies and music, which creates an immersive atmosphere.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SOULS LIKE ELEMENTS</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/souls-like.GIF?t=1745014980\" /></span><br><br>The game introduces mechanics typical of Souls Like games, such as challenging fights with enemies, a system of dying and learning from mistakes, and the need to develop effective strategies to defeat enemies and survive in a hostile world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DUNGEON EXPLORATION</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/76652c931ac83d1c1747af16ec435842.poster.avif?t=1745014980\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/76652c931ac83d1c1747af16ec435842.webm?t=1745014980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134790/extras/76652c931ac83d1c1747af16ec435842.mp4?t=1745014980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Dreadborne Dungeon is also a classic dungeon crawler, in which players traverse dark dungeons. Each step can lead to new challenges and surprises.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SATISFACTORY DIFFICULTY</strong></h2>The game sets a high level of difficulty that rewards patience and determination. Every failure is an opportunity to learn and improve your skills, which gives great satisfaction from every success achieved.<br><br>Traverse dark dungeons, fight dangerous opponents and face numerous challenges. Die, draw conclusions and don't give up! Good luck!",
